             was indicted for <rs id="t17931030-24-off131" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17931030-24-off131" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17931030-24-off131" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17931030-24-cd132" type="crimeDate">27th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17931030-24-off131 t17931030-24-cd132"></join>, a pewter pint pot, value 1 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17931030-24-victim261" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Steward
                  <interp inst="t17931030-24-victim261" type="surname" value="Steward"></interp>
